Version 2.0.1
  * Tweaked colour scheme.
Version 2.0.0
  * New colour scheme
  * Animation toggle removed from main menu
  * Change colour now modifies the whole colour scheme
  * Added mass addition & subtraction to advanced maths
  * Added 'about' option to main menu
  * General code cleanup
Version 1.2.1
  * Fixed a bug causing the advanced calculations menu to be unreturnable.
Version 1.2.0
  * Now uses MB++ 3.0 beta 1 library, improves menu drawing efficiency.
Version 1.1.0
  * Created a new main menu.
  * All old functions are in "Simple Calculations"
  * Add Square/Cube function.
  * Added Power function.
  * Added ability to change border colour.
  * Added ability to toggle animations.
Version 1.0.2
  * Division by zero now gives an error via MB++ "ERRBOX" function, rather than freezing.
  * Updated from MB++ version 2.1.0 to 2.1.5 for smoother animations.
Version 1.0.1
  * Added "Exit" button since "MENUBOX" from MB++ no-longer supports using the escape key to end.
Version 1.0.0
  * Initial Release
